<% pageTitle = 'About — FatSwitchDiet'; metaDesc = 'The story behind FatSwitchDiet and the Fat Switch method.'; canonicalUrl = '/about'; %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<div class="static-hero"><h1>About FatSwitchDiet</h1><p>The story behind the switch</p></div>
<div class="static-content">
  <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px">
    <div style="width:120px;height:120px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--amber),var(--forest));margin:0 auto 16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:3.5rem">👩‍🍳</div>
    <h2 style="margin-top:0">Hi, I'm Alex Rivera</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-light);font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:0.9rem">Nutritionist, Recipe Developer & Founder of FatSwitchDiet</p>
  </div>
  <p>I grew up eating the most indulgent, delicious food you can imagine — rich pastas, stuffed breads, creamy curries, fried everything. Food wasn't just fuel in my family. It was love, culture, and connection.</p>
  <p>When I studied nutrition, I expected to learn how to give all of that up. Instead, I learned something far more powerful: <strong>you don't have to.</strong></p>
  <h2>What is the Fat Switch?</h2>
  <p>The "Fat Switch" is our core methodology. For every recipe, we identify the specific ingredients that add the most calories and saturated fat, then find a swap that preserves the cooking chemistry, maintains the same flavor, and significantly reduces calories — typically 30–45%.</p>
  <h2>The AI Generator</h2>
  <p>We built an AI-powered recipe generator so you can get a full Fat Switch recipe for <em>any</em> dish, instantly. Type a recipe name, and our AI creates a complete recipe with ingredient swaps, nutrition comparison, and a shareable page — in under 15 seconds.</p>
  <p><a href="/generator" class="btn btn-primary" style="display:inline-flex;margin-top:8px">⚡ Try the Generator →</a></p>
  <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
  <p>Have a recipe request or question? <a href="/contact">Contact us here</a>.</p>
  <div style="background:var(--forest);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:32px;text-align:center;margin-top:40px">
    <p style="color:var(--cream);font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:4px"><em>"Every indulgent recipe has a smarter version. My job is to find it."</em></p>
    <p style="color:var(--amber-light);font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:0.85rem">— Alex Rivera, FatSwitchDiet</p>
  </div>
</div>
